## MergerFS
/Volumes/Media[A-Z]     /Volumes/Media            fuse.mergerfs defaults,category.create=mspmfs,allow_other,minfreespace=50G,fsname=MediaFS,nonempty,moveonenospc=true,func.getattr=newest,use_ino,noforget,inodecalc=path-hash 0 0
# create policy "mspmfs == Of all the branches on which the relative path exists choose the drive with the most free space. but walk back the path if it fails to find a branch at that level.
# minfreespace == filter the drive out of consideration for create requests, but doesn't cause any errors when writing
# moveonnospc == move files according to policy IF it generates a filesystem full error
# nonempty == allow mounting over non-empty directories (/Volumes/Media). Allows for upgrading Mergerfs
#inodecalc=path-hash,useino,noforget to fix NFS export of Media
#func.getattr=newset to fix directory mtime for Plex scanning
#If wanting to use Plex DB on MediaFS, add dropcacheonclose=true to disable direct_ii
#=#=# END WILLFLIX
